      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POINT BREAK (3) has been out of the placings at his last couple of runs but impressed when posting a convincing 25.67 over 460m at this track three starts back. Hard to top on best recent times. BRINDLE SURPRISE (2) boasts a consistent overall record including 10 wins from 35 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when third (35.19) over 595m at Sandown. Solid record here winning two races. Expected to feature on best form. DR. FANATICAL (1) was well in the market last time but only managed seventh (30.57), beaten 22 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Got the money at his only try from this box. Expected to give a good account. PAW JASTA (8) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
